Package org.biohipi.imagebundle

Classes for storing and manipulating collections of images.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BioHipiImageBundle
    A BioHipiImageBundle (BioHIB) is the primary representation for a collection of biomedical images on the Hadoop Distributed File System (HDFS) used by BioHIPI.
    BioHipiImageBundle.BioHibReader
    This FileReader enables reading individual images from a BioHipiImageBundle and delivers them in the specified image type.
